    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><strong>Material 3 / Apple HIG / Fluent 2</strong></td>
      <td>Qualitative principles (clarity, consistency, hierarchy) <em>plus hard accessibility floors</em>: WCAG AA 4.5:1 contrast, 44–48px touch targets. None ships a scored critique form.</td>
      <td>The deterministic <em>thresholds</em>; the vendor gap is exactly what a scored rubric fills.</td>
    </tr>
